4
00:00:13,212 --> 00:00:15,876
In this first module on 
plasma astrophysics,

5
00:00:15,876 --> 00:00:21,105
we will deal with the most powerful source
of energy in our solar system: the Sun.

6
00:00:21,723 --> 00:00:26,043
Today we will answer some 
fundamental questions about our Sun.

7
00:00:26,371 --> 00:00:27,778
What powers the Sun?

8
00:00:27,778 --> 00:00:29,283
How does it shine?

9
00:00:29,283 --> 00:00:32,662
We will address these questions 
in a simplified way by using

10
00:00:32,662 --> 00:00:36,286
the fundamental tools of plasma physics 
